---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Kids | Iglesia Corazon de Fuego">
  <Navbar sticky={false} />

  <main class="kids-page">
    <section class="kids-hero">
      <div class="kids-hero-glow kids-hero-glow-right"></div>
      <div class="kids-hero-glow kids-hero-glow-left"></div>

      <div class="kids-shell kids-hero-grid">
        <div class="kids-copy">
          <div class="kids-badge">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">rocket_launch</span>
            <span>NUEVA AVENTURA DISPONIBLE</span>
          </div>

          <h1 class="kids-title">
            ¡Bienvenido al lugar <span>más divertido!</span>
          </h1>

          <p class="kids-lead">
            Un espacio vibrante donde cada niño descubre que es un héroe en la gran historia de Dios.
          </p>

          <div class="kids-actions">
            <button class="kids-button kids-button-primary">
              <span>Quiero jugar y aprender</span>
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined">sports_esports</span>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="kids-hero-media">
          <div class="kids-hero-card">
            <img
              alt="Campa Kids"
              src="/ministries/kids/campakids.jpg"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="kids-float kids-float-star">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">star</span>
          </div>

          <div class="kids-float kids-float-party">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">celebration</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="kids-age-section">
      <div class="kids-shell">
        <div class="kids-section-heading">
          <h2>Salitas</h2>
          <p>Cada grupo comparte actividades pensadas para su edad, con enseñanza, juego y acompañamiento.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="kids-age-grid">
          <article class="kids-age-card kids-age-card-blue">
            <div class="kids-age-image">
              <img
                alt="Toddlers playing"
                src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCjV8mD6mpuXtkOV78FyuzNWp6qHG8cg_0SzBO6sZn-mdr-9S7nmV8RgSU15E9wViR3teH_kx4RmZ1AmTMzKlZUsmbwnC7OHbue7so9k2YTbutAN6mYSmciw6AdrBrlg_CSdZoRUHnNWRZrSCQEdN25Q3vK1N7R3kUU88X1UjI8sx0RtAc4tSkE82wP-f-5AsXcNKx-TSCxf_BrE4dQ2ADYInkaLwC75s-dUlJ13eYsxlJijWly-1ug_0X6MVdSwgAE4qu7GyJZnaw"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="kids-age-copy">
              <span class="kids-chip kids-chip-blue">Salita 1</span>
              <h3>3 a 4 años</h3>
              <p>Una propuesta suave y visual para sus primeros pasos: canciones, cuentos bíblicos y actividades simples.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="kids-age-card kids-age-card-pink">
            <div class="kids-age-image">
              <img
                alt="Older kids activity"
                src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBsUiu0w_-kL1IpN33j2OGsyLWZDIriCvmYfIhB9Ju8LhurQptVwVBmoW3gHkyQK6uSPWPuHKRddT5vENjjFAm6r55JBpWXJi2pUjDRylRfbc0igxurItv90Mwjk8_erVPs87Btbvc3ns7gjQXQmKBxkyj9sYt8jOwDnwAMHyLix9AEtRkC48ySoSRsw70Vu5C4y6gjoyN4r85Erhv6skaENiIg20yYdhny1o55AkBVRMt4bZlJLZOjFHdXlUkPdcrFOE5USa4t0w4"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="kids-age-copy">
              <span class="kids-chip kids-chip-pink">Salita 2</span>
              <h3>5 a 7 años</h3>
              <p>Aprenden con más participación, juegos grupales, memoria bíblica y momentos de oración guiada.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="kids-age-card kids-age-card-yellow">
            <div class="kids-age-image">
              <img
                alt="Kids group activity"
                src="/ministries/kids/kids.png"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="kids-age-copy">
              <span class="kids-chip kids-chip-yellow">Salita 3</span>
              <h3>8 a 10 años</h3>
              <p>Un espacio con más desafíos, conversación, trabajo en equipo y aplicación práctica de la enseñanza.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="kids-parents-section">
      <div class="kids-shell kids-parents-grid">
        <div class="kids-parents-copy">
          <span class="kids-parents-badge">Equipo y dinámica</span>
          <h2>¿Cómo se desarrolla la actividad?</h2>
          <p>
            Cada reunión está organizada para que los chicos estén bien acompañados, aprendan con claridad y disfruten el tiempo en su salita.
          </p>

          <div class="kids-parent-list">
            <article>
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined">person_raised_hand</span>
              <div>
                <h5>Líderes por salita</h5>
                <p>Cada grupo tiene referentes que dirigen la enseñanza, ordenan la actividad y acompañan a los chicos durante toda la reunión.</p>
              </div>
            </article>

            <article class="kids-parent-list-blue">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined">groups</span>
              <div>
                <h5>Ayudantes y apoyo</h5>
                <p>Además de los líderes, hay ayudantes que reciben, contienen, asisten en juegos, materiales y acompañamiento general.</p>
              </div>
            </article>

            <article class="kids-parent-list-yellow">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined">schedule</span>
              <div>
                <h5>Desarrollo de la reunión</h5>
                <p>Bienvenida, alabanza, enseñanza bíblica, actividad por edades y cierre en un entorno cuidado y dinámico.</p>
              </div>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="kids-family-wrap">
          <div class="kids-family-image">
            <img
              alt="Happy family"
              src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAPU4bDMgrMKWNCeVVMUAhGl2urJbhJRpm_klWmYbZMOEsaOpBKEmUWBZ_TN5UOBVMHi-8WfcMaBztjC81I1EWEM-Gj6mU3zj3dL32EweyY0NdAJwuGic0DyxVpBSnakZC1Fc-MzITSYO2WnIETtgaaapZu9IdO1sYACYESAURflFhoVD3Vh66WbrFnlVZledxTQpkQGI2XusFQ-HwfgId-G5I_eQTHiC7D_y8H9IPCz8JfxdGZLwZ0Z37DF7LR1trxC3UknFQbRPA"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="kids-family-stat">
            <span>3</span>
            <small>Salitas por edades</small>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />

  <style>
    .kids-page {
      background: #fbf4ff;
      color: #37018f;
      font-family: 'Be Vietnam Pro', 'Inter', sans-serif;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    .kids-page .material-symbols-outlined {
      font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0, 'wght' 400, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24;
    }

    .kids-shell {
      width: min(100% - 3rem, 1440px);
      margin-inline: auto;
    }

    .kids-hero {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 820px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 3rem 0 6rem;
    }

    .kids-hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 3rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .kids-hero-glow {
      position: absolute;
      z-index: 0;
      filter: blur(60px);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .kids-hero-glow-right {
      top: 0;
      right: 0;
      width: 50%;
      height: 100%;
      border-bottom-left-radius: 10rem;
      background: rgba(134, 203, 255, 0.2);
    }

    .kids-hero-glow-left {
      left: -5rem;
      bottom: -5rem;
      width: 20rem;
      height: 20rem;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      background: rgba(255, 133, 228, 0.3);
    }

    .kids-copy,
    .kids-hero-media {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .kids-copy {
      max-width: 42rem;
    }

    .kids-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      background: #a7d7ff;
      color: #004c71;
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    .kids-title,
    .kids-age-copy h3,
    .kids-event-content h2,
    .kids-videos-head h2,
    .kids-video-card h4,
    .kids-parents-copy h2 {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
    }

    .kids-title {
      margin: 2rem 0 0;
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6.25rem);
      line-height: 0.98;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #37018f;
    }

    .kids-title span {
      color: #a80096;
    }

    .kids-lead {
      max-width: 34rem;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2.5vw, 1.65rem);
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #6544bd;
    }

    .kids-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding-top: 1rem;
    }

    .kids-button {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      border: 0;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.25s ease, background-color 0.25s ease, color 0.25s ease;
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .kids-button:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .kids-button-primary {
      padding: 1.25rem 2.5rem;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6d5a00, #fdd400);
      color: #433700;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(55, 1, 143, 0.16);
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .kids-button-light {
      padding: 1.25rem 3rem;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      background: #fff;
      color: #37018f;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .kids-button-light:hover {
      background: #fdd400;
    }

    .kids-button-pink {
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      background: #a80096;
      color: white;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .kids-button-pink:hover {
      background: #940084;
    }

    .kids-hero-media {
      position: relative;
      width: min(100%, 36rem);
      margin-left: auto;
    }

    .kids-hero-card {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 3.25rem;
      box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(55, 1, 143, 0.14);
      transform: rotate(1deg);
      transition: transform 0.7s ease;
    }

    .kids-hero-card:hover {
      transform: rotate(0deg);
    }

    .kids-hero-card img {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      height: 540px;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: center top;
    }

    .kids-float {
      position: absolute;
      z-index: 2;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(55, 1, 143, 0.16);
    }

    .kids-float-star {
      top: -1.5rem;
      right: -1.5rem;
      width: 6.5rem;
      height: 6.5rem;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      background: #fdd400;
      animation: kids-bounce 2.2s infinite;
    }

    .kids-float-star .material-symbols-outlined {
      font-size: 2.4rem;
      color: #594a00;
      font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1, 'wght' 500, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24;
    }

    .kids-float-party {
      left: -1rem;
      bottom: -1rem;
      width: 4.75rem;
      height: 4.75rem;
      border-radius: 1.25rem;
      background: #a80096;
      transform: rotate(12deg);
    }

    .kids-float-party .material-symbols-outlined {
      font-size: 1.9rem;
      color: white;
    }

    .kids-age-section {
      padding: 6rem 0;
      background: #f5eeff;
      border-radius: 5rem;
    }

    .kids-section-heading {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .kids-section-heading h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #37018f;
    }

    .kids-section-heading p,
    .kids-videos-head p,
    .kids-video-card p,
    .kids-parents-copy p {
      color: #6544bd;
    }

    .kids-section-heading p {
      margin: 1rem 0 0;
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }

    .kids-age-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .kids-age-card {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2rem;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 3rem;
      border: 2px solid transparent;
      background: white;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(55, 1, 143, 0.06);
      transition: all 0.5s ease;
    }

    .kids-age-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 22px 40px rgba(55, 1, 143, 0.1);
    }

    .kids-age-card-blue:hover {
      border-color: #a7d7ff;
    }

    .kids-age-card-pink:hover {
      border-color: #ff85e4;
    }

    .kids-age-card-yellow:hover {
      border-color: #fdd400;
    }

    .kids-age-image {
      width: 12rem;
      height: 12rem;
      overflow: hidden;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      border-radius: 2rem;
    }

    .kids-age-card-blue .kids-age-image {
      background: #a7d7ff;
    }

    .kids-age-card-pink .kids-age-image {
      background: #ff85e4;
    }

    .kids-age-card-yellow .kids-age-image {
      background: #fdd400;
    }

    .kids-age-image img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      transition: transform 0.5s ease;
    }

    .kids-age-card:hover .kids-age-image img {
      transform: scale(1.1);
    }

    .kids-chip {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.35rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    }

    .kids-chip-blue {
      background: #00618f;
      color: #eaf4ff;
    }

    .kids-chip-pink {
      background: #a80096;
      color: #ffeef6;
    }

    .kids-chip-yellow {
      background: #fdd400;
      color: #433700;
    }

    .kids-age-copy h3 {
      margin: 1rem 0 0;
      font-size: 1.9rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .kids-age-copy {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .kids-age-card-blue h3,
    .kids-age-card-blue .kids-link {
      color: #00618f;
    }

    .kids-age-card-pink h3,
    .kids-age-card-pink .kids-link {
      color: #a80096;
    }

    .kids-age-card-yellow h3,
    .kids-age-card-yellow .kids-link {
      color: #6d5a00;
    }

    .kids-age-copy p {
      margin: 1rem 0 0;
      color: #6544bd;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .kids-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: gap 0.3s ease;
    }

    .kids-age-card:hover .kids-link {
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .kids-parents-section {
      padding: 6rem 0;
      background: rgba(255, 133, 228, 0.1);
    }

    .kids-parents-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 4rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .kids-parents-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.65rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      background: rgba(168, 0, 150, 0.1);
      color: #a80096;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .kids-parents-copy h2 {
      margin: 1.5rem 0 0;
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #37018f;
    }

    .kids-parents-copy > p {
      margin: 1.5rem 0 0;
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .kids-parent-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    .kids-parent-list article {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 1rem;
      border-left: 4px solid #a80096;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      background: white;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 22px rgba(55, 1, 143, 0.08);
    }

    .kids-parent-list-blue {
      border-left-color: #00618f !important;
    }

    .kids-parent-list-yellow {
      border-left-color: #fdd400 !important;
    }

    .kids-parent-list article .material-symbols-outlined {
      color: #a80096;
    }

    .kids-parent-list-blue .material-symbols-outlined {
      color: #00618f !important;
    }

    .kids-parent-list-yellow .material-symbols-outlined {
      color: #6d5a00 !important;
    }

    .kids-parent-list h5 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #37018f;
    }

    .kids-parent-list p {
      margin: 0.3rem 0 0;
      color: #6544bd;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    .kids-family-wrap {
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .kids-family-image {
      width: min(100%, 400px);
      aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      border: 12px solid #fff;
      background: #a80096;
      box-shadow: 0 24px 50px rgba(55, 1, 143, 0.18);
    }

    .kids-family-image img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .kids-family-stat {
      position: absolute;
      right: 0;
      bottom: -1.5rem;
      max-width: 200px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      background: white;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 36px rgba(55, 1, 143, 0.14);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .kids-family-stat span {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1.875rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #a80096;
    }

    .kids-family-stat small {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: #6544bd;
    }

    @keyframes kids-bounce {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
    }

    @media (min-width: 1024px) {
      .kids-hero-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.08fr) minmax(0, 0.92fr);
      }

      .kids-age-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }

      .kids-age-card {
        flex-direction: row;
      }

      .kids-parents-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }

    @media (min-width: 1280px) {
      .kids-age-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }

      .kids-age-card {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .kids-age-image {
        width: 100%;
        height: 15rem;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 767px) {
      .kids-shell {
        width: min(100% - 2rem, 1536px);
      }

      .kids-hero {
        min-height: auto;
        padding: 2rem 0 5rem;
      }

      .kids-title {
        font-size: clamp(2.3rem, 14vw, 4.25rem);
        line-height: 0.98;
      }

      .kids-lead {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }

      .kids-button-primary {
        width: 100%;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .kids-hero-media {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .kids-hero-card {
        border-radius: 2.5rem;
        transform: none;
      }

      .kids-hero-card img {
        height: 330px;
      }

      .kids-float-star {
        top: 0.75rem;
        right: 0.75rem;
        width: 4.5rem;
        height: 4.5rem;
      }

      .kids-float-star .material-symbols-outlined {
        font-size: 1.9rem;
      }

      .kids-float-party {
        display: none;
      }

      .kids-age-section,
      .kids-parents-section {
        padding: 4rem 0;
      }

      .kids-age-section {
        border-radius: 2.5rem;
      }

      .kids-family-stat {
        left: 50%;
        right: auto;
        bottom: -2rem;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        width: min(100%, 12rem);
      }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
